51
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,840
What!?

52
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:30,640
Hitomi!

53
00:04:31,790 --> 00:04:35,280
- That girl is always so selfish!
- Come on now!

54
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,860
