121
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:04,800
Um...

122
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,670
Nishi...

123
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:15,520
Stay there! One million volts!

124
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:35,050
I always worried that you might come to hate me.

125
00:10:35,770 --> 00:10:38,490
But when I see your face,

126
00:10:38,490 --> 00:10:40,970
I can't hold myself back.

127
00:10:46,710 --> 00:10:50,930
I want to move forward.

128
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:55,610
I want to go as far as possible as I can.

129
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:04,720
With you, Y-Yuki.

130
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:08,940
- If you're going to stutter, then stop.
- Huh?

131
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,960
Calling me by my first name.

132
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,940
Sorry.

133
00:11:14,510 --> 00:11:16,250
It's fine.

134
00:11:23,070 --> 00:11:25,390
I told you, it's fine!

135
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,380
But...

136
00:11:42,050 --> 00:11:44,860
if I cross this line,

137
00:11:44,860 --> 00:11:47,040
I'll be electrocuted to death.

138
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:58,220
If you're not the one to come here and kiss me...

139
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:09,050
Don't move.

140
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:25,400
Don't look at me!

141
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,290
Akira.

142
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,520
Say it again.

143
00:12:53,980 --> 00:12:55,660
Akira.

144
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,690
I love you.

145
00:13:34,060 --> 00:13:36,490
You don't really have to send me off.

146
00:13:36,490 --> 00:13:38,550
Well...

147
00:13:40,200 --> 00:13:42,010
I wanted to send you off!

148
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:49,700
- Is your health all right?
- Yeah.

149
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:58,520
Here is fine.

150
00:14:00,430 --> 00:14:02,110
Okay.

151
00:14:03,890 --> 00:14:05,490
See you.

152
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:26,290
Akira.

153
00:14:27,030 --> 00:14:28,770
Big Sis!

154
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:34,340
Was that your lover?

155
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:38,130
Huh?

156
00:14:48,130 --> 00:14:49,600
Yeah.

157
00:14:52,260 --> 00:14:54,820
What is it? Cut it out!

158
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:58,060
I'm happy that

159
00:14:58,060 --> 00:15:01,780
you're finally living honestly with yourself.

160
00:15:07,360 --> 00:15:09,340
Let's go home already.

161
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:10,810
Okay.

162
00:15:20,190 --> 00:15:22,360
I don't know where

163
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,060
this line leads to.

164
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:31,250
However, if we're together, surely...

