201
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:43,730
Just try it on!

202
00:17:43,730 --> 00:17:45,980
It's important to get the right size!

203
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:47,210
Right?

204
00:17:47,210 --> 00:17:48,510
That's correct!

205
00:17:48,510 --> 00:17:51,660
- That's what's important?
- Yeah.

206
00:17:58,150 --> 00:17:59,760
Is this fine?

207
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:06,560
That suits you quite well.

208
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,670
I'll adjust the hems.

209
00:18:11,570 --> 00:18:14,290
Akira, how is it?

210
00:18:15,100 --> 00:18:19,770
Well, it's really nice.

211
00:18:21,900 --> 00:18:23,490
- Really?
- Yeah.

212
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:26,570
I mean...

213
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:29,480
It's kind of sexy.

214
00:18:30,050 --> 00:18:32,590
This should do it.

215
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:47,140
You know,

216
00:18:47,140 --> 00:18:50,100
I can't imagine it.

217
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:51,650
What?

218
00:18:51,650 --> 00:18:53,930
Myself, as a working adult.

219
00:18:53,930 --> 00:18:57,910
I have nothing I'm good at and nothing I want to do.

220
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:02,630
Everyone else has a goal they're running towards.

221
00:19:02,630 --> 00:19:05,500
I'm the only one who's unsure.

222
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:10,940
I end up just following everyone else.

223
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:15,890
And if I just end up going somewhere because of that...

224
00:19:15,890 --> 00:19:18,040
Would that be okay?

225
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:23,010
I really badly want to become a working adult.

226
00:19:24,590 --> 00:19:26,560
I guess that...

227
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:29,230
your sense is just worlds apart from mine.

228
00:19:29,230 --> 00:19:32,370
If we become working adults, we can live together, can't we?

229
00:19:34,560 --> 00:19:37,410
Then we can be together every day.

230
00:19:39,220 --> 00:19:42,800
That's my goal.

231
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:51,440
Everyone has their own reasons for working.

232
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:56,810
I see.

233
00:20:12,130 --> 00:20:14,380
We can live together.

234
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:16,660
Yeah, you don't want to?

235
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:18,460
No, I do.

236
00:20:20,230 --> 00:20:24,390
- We all have our reasons for working, right?
- Shut up!

237
00:20:55,700 --> 00:20:57,830
I'm back.

238
00:20:57,830 --> 00:20:59,150
I'm so tired.

239
00:20:59,150 --> 00:21:01,740
Welcome back, I just finished making our meal.

240
00:21:01,740 --> 00:21:04,140
Awesome!

241
00:21:07,120 --> 00:21:08,330
Are you hungry?

242
00:21:08,330 --> 00:21:11,560
- I'm starving!
- Here's a big serving of stir-fried vegetables and meat.

243
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:14,290
That looks delicious!

244
00:21:14,290 --> 00:21:15,880
It smells great!

245
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:17,530
Thank you!

246
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,300
It's great!
[Twenty-five]

247
00:21:19,360 --> 00:21:22,420
Yummy!

248
00:21:22,420 --> 00:21:24,510
Delicious!

249
00:21:24,540 --> 00:21:26,620
- Amazing!
- You're praising yourself.

250
00:21:26,620 --> 00:21:27,850
As expected of me!

251
00:21:27,850 --> 00:21:30,710
[Akari Corporation]

252
00:21:32,780 --> 00:21:34,190
Hey, Itou!

253
00:21:34,190 --> 00:21:36,400
- Can I have a moment?
- Yes.

254
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:40,270
This is Ms. Shiraishi, who has joined the company part way through the year.

255
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,540
Please take care of me.

256
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:53,290
I like you, please go out with me.

257
00:21:53,290 --> 00:21:57,310
If there's anything you don't understand, please ask him.

258
00:21:57,310 --> 00:21:59,510
- Okay.
- I'm counting on you!

259
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,880
Okay.

260
00:22:03,730 --> 00:22:05,980
Please treat me kindly.

261
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:12,480
Me as well.

262
00:22:26,210 --> 00:22:30,690
Itou-kun, I like you.

263
00:22:31,450 --> 00:22:34,000
I found some gold in the desert!

264
00:22:35,750 --> 00:22:37,370
Let's break up.

